 ROLE OF INSTITUTES FOR FURTHER EDUCATION IN THE IMPLEMENTATION OF NEWTECHNICAL AND SCIENTIFIC METHODS.THE ROLE PLAYED BY INSTITUTES FOR FURTHER EDUCATION IN THE ECONOMIC STRATEGYOF THE USSR IS DEMONSTRATED BY THE EXAMPLE OF THE EDUCATIONAL PROGRAMME OF THEINSTITUTE FOR FURTHER EDUCATION OF INFORMATION SCIENTISTS. THE MAIN GOAL OFTHE EDUCATIONAL PROGRAMME OF THIS INSTITUTE IS TO INCREASE THE EFFECTIVENESSOF THE STATE SCIENTIFIC AND TECHNICAL INFORMATION SYSTEM. THE EDUCATIONALPROGRAMME IS DISCUSSED WITH PARTICULAR EMPHASIS ON IMPLEMENTATION OF ADVANCEDWORKING METHODS AND ON THE COOPERATION OF LECTURERS WITH EXPERTS IN VARIOUSFIELDS OF SCIENCE AND TECHNOLOGY